een gushing out from under the earth. He also closed up the sky, and the rain stopped. "}, {:version=>"Good News Translation", :text=>"The outlets of the water beneath the earth and the floodgates of the sky were closed. The rain stopped, "}, {:version=>"Holman Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"The sources of the watery depths and the floodgates of the sky were closed, and the rain from the sky stopped."}, {:version=>"International Standard Version", :text=>"The water sources from the ocean depths were blocked and the floodgates of the heavens were closed. "}, {:version=>"NET Bible", :text=>"The fountains of the deep and the floodgates of heaven were closed, and the rain stopped falling from the sky."}, {:version=>"New Heart English Bible", :text=>"And the fountains of the deep and the floodgates of the sky were closed, and the rain from the sky was restrained."}, {:version=>"GOD'S WORD® Translation", :text=>"The deep springs and the sky had been shut, and the rain had stopped pouring."}, {:version=>"JPS Tanakh 1917", :text=>"the fountains also of the deep and the windows of heaven were stopped, and the rain from heaven was restrained."}, {:version=>"New American Standard 1977 ", :text=>"Also the fountains of the deep and the floodgates of the sky were closed, and the rain from the sky was restrained;"}, {:version=>"King James 2000 Bible", :text=>"The fountains also of the deep and the windows of heaven were stopped, and the rain from heaven was restrained;"}, {:version=>"American King James Version", :text=>"The fountains also of the deep and the windows of heaven were stopped, and the rain from heaven was restrained;"}, {:version=>"American Standard Version", :text=>"the fountains also of the deep and the windows of heaven were stopped, and the rain from heaven was restrained;"}, {:version=>"Brenton Septuagint Translation", :text=>"And the fountains of the deep were closed up, and the flood-gates of heaven, and the rain from heaven was withheld."}, {:version=>"Do